OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FVictims abused by referee  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FHugh Stevenson say the SFA 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fis blocking justice        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Two men who were sexually abused by an 
OL,6, assistant referee in the 1970s have    
OL,7, said Scottish football's governing body
OL,8, is standing in the way of justice.     
OL,10,FPeter Haynes and Stuart McMillan said  
OL,11,Fthe SFA was refusing to accept any     
OL,12,Fliability for what happened to them.   
OL,14,FThe men were children when they were   
OL,15,Ftargeted by Hugh Stevenson.            
OL,17,FHe was an SFA-accredited top flight    
OL,18,Fmatch official between 1963 and 1984,  
OL,19,Fas well as a youth football coach. He  
OL,20,Fdied in 2004, aged 66.                 
